    <body>
        To complete this quiz, please fill out this questionnaire below. When done click submit. <br>
        <form method="post" action=<%- action %>>

            QUESTION 1: You see a classmate who dropped his books in the hallway. What do you do?
            <select name="q1">
                <option>Help them pick up their books</option>
