            <select name="q2">
                <option>Start it today, get it over with fast.</option>
                <option>Work on it gradually throughout the month</option>
                <option>Do it the day before</option>
                <option></option>
            </select> <br>

            QUESTION 3: Which of these traits best describe you?
            <select name="q3">
                <option>brave</option>
                <option>cunning</option>
                <option>clever</option>
            </select> <br>
            
            Name (to be stored in database):<input name="username" type="text"><br>
